## Common Issues and Fixes

### Issue: Axe not running
**Cause:** Not initialized or not in dev mode  
**Fix:** Call `axeService.initializeAxe()` in AppComponent ngOnInit

### Issue: Components not found
**Cause:** AccessibilityModule not imported  
**Fix:** Import AccessibilityModule in your module

### Issue: ESLint a11y rules not working
**Cause:** Plugin not installed or configured  
**Fix:** Check that eslint-plugin-angular-a11y is in package.json and .eslintrc.json

### Issue: Skip link not working
**Cause:** Target element doesn't have ID or tabindex  
**Fix:** Add \`id\` and \`tabindex="-1"\` to target element

## Examples

### Modal with Focus Trap
\`\`\`html
<div class="modal-backdrop" *ngIf="isModalOpen" (click)="closeModal()">
  <div class="modal-content" appFocusTrap [isActive]="isModalOpen" (click)="$event.stopPropagation()">
    <h2 id="modal-title">Modal Title</h2>
    <p>Modal content...</p>
    <button (click)="closeModal()">Close</button>
  </div>
</div>
\`\`\`

### Form with Live Validation
\`\`\`html
<form>
  <label for="email">Email:</label>
  <input 
    id="email" 
    type="email" 
    [(ngModel)]="email" 
    name="email"
    (blur)="validateEmail()"
    [attr.aria-invalid]="emailError ? 'true' : null"
    [attr.aria-describedby]="emailError ? 'email-error' : null">
  
  <app-live-region 
    *ngIf="emailError"
    id="email-error"
    [message]="emailError" 
    ariaLive="assertive"
    class="error">
  </app-live-region>
</form>
\`\`\`

### Data Table with Screen Reader Support
\`\`\`html
<table>
  <caption>User List</caption>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th scope="col">Name</th>
      <th scope="col">Email</th>
      <th scope="col">Role</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr *ngFor="let user of users">
      <td>{{ user.name }}</td>
      <td>{{ user.email }}</td>
      <td>{{ user.role }}</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
\`\`\`

